### Describe the bug

Application failed to start when upgrading Quarkus from 2.5.1 to 2.7.1.

Default constructor is removed since 2.6:
* https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/2.5/independent-projects/resteasy-reactive/server/runtime/src/main/java/org/jboss/resteasy/reactive/server/core/parameters/converters/LocalDateParamConverter.java
* https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/2.6/independent-projects/resteasy-reactive/server/runtime/src/main/java/org/jboss/resteasy/reactive/server/core/parameters/converters/LocalDateParamConverter.java


```java
import java.time.LocalDate;
import javax.ws.rs.QueryParam;

public class SummaryRequest {

  @QueryParam("tradeDate")
  private LocalDate tradeDate;

  public LocalDate getTradeDate() {
    return tradeDate;
  }

  public void setTradeDate(LocalDate tradeDate) {
    this.tradeDate = tradeDate;
  }
}
```

```java
import java.util.concurrent.CompletionStage;
import javax.validation.Valid;
import javax.ws.rs.BeanParam;
import javax.ws.rs.GET;
import javax.ws.rs.Path;

public interface TradeResource {

  @Path("/summary")
  @GET
  CompletionStage<SummaryResponse> getSummary(@Valid @BeanParam SummaryRequest request);
}
```

### Expected behavior

Application starts successfully

### Actual behavior

Application failed to start with below stacktrace:

